-- Hyundai Motor to appeal chairman's jail sentence
-- 
-- Mon Feb 5, 2007 2:56am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/05/uk-hyundai-chairman-appeal-idUSSEO33527320070205

 

 SEOUL  (Reuters) - Hyundai Motor plans to appeal against a court ruling on Monday sentencing the automotive group's chairman to three years in jail, a company spokesman said. 


 "We are greatly disappointed by the court ruling today. It is our intention to file an appeal," said Jake Jang, a Hyundai Motor spokesman.